Ok Ok, don't yell at me. Did a Google search best pizza in NYC. Lombardi's comes up. Not sure why. wait time said 20 took 35 Saturday afternoon. 4-2-2011. Staff were friendly , efficient. pizza over all flavor 1-10 10 the highest my opinion a 6. sauce was a bit bland, doe was good peperoni was small sized. cheese was not flavorful, Sorry folks this is my Truth, would recommend other places first. Maybe years ago they were the leader in my view, will never go back or recommend.. S
